<法規>
<法規性質>命令</法規性質>
<英文法規名稱>Standards for Types and Tolerance Levels of Pathogenic Microorganisms and Health-hazard Materials in Pet Food</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>寵物食品病原微生物與有害健康物質種類及安全容許量標準</中文法規名稱>
<法規網址>http://law.moj.gov.tw/Eng/LawClass/LawContent.aspx?PCODE=M0060081</法規網址>
<最新英文異動日期>20161209</最新英文異動日期>
<廢止註記>
</廢止註記>
<沿革內容><![CDATA[1. Promulgated on No. 1040043099A on 5th August 2015
2. Article 5 were amended and promulgated on No. 1050043642A on 9 December 2016.]]></沿革內容>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards are stipulated in accordance with the provisions of the second paragraph of Article 22-4 of the Animal Protection Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The terms in the Standards are defined as follows:
1.Amount of aflatoxins: the sum of total amount of B1, B2, G1 and G2 aflatoxins.
2.ppb: micrograms per kilogram.
3.ppm: milligrams per kilogram.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The following pathogenic microorganisms shall not be detected nor contained in pet food:
1.Salmonella spp.
2.Listeria monocytogenes
3.Pathogenic Escherichia coli
4.Clostridium perfringens
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The amount of aflatoxins in pet food shall not exceed 20 ppb.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The amount of heavy metals in pet food shall not exceed:
1.Arsenic:
(1)Feed for pet animals containing aquatic animals, seaweed, and products derived thereof and/or meal: maximum content in mg/kg (ppm) relative to a feed with a moisture content of 12 % at 10 ppm and inorganic arsenic is under 2 ppm.
(2)Others: 2 ppm.
2.Cadmium: 2 ppm
3.Lead: 5 ppm
4.Mercury: 0.4 ppm
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The amount of  pesticide residues in pet food shall not exceed:
1.Aldrin and Dieldrin: 0.01 ppm
2.BHC: 0.01 ppm
3.DDT: 0.1 ppm
4.Endrin: 0.01ppm
5.Heptachlor: 0.01 ppm
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 7</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The amount of preservatives and antioxidants in pet food shall not exceed:
1.Total content of ethoxyquin, Butylated hydroxytoluene (BHT) and Butylated hydroxyanisole (BHA) is 150ppm, and ethoxyquin shall not be more than 75 ppm.
2.Sodium nitrite: 100 ppm
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 8</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The amount of health-hazard materials in pet food shall not exceed:
1.Melamine: 2.5 ppm
2.Propylene glycol: shall not be detected in cat food.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 9</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards shall come into force on the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
